basis make things nice?

30
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,330
It certainly does.

31
00:02:00,330 --> 00:02:02,490
It makes all the
calculations better,

32
00:02:02,490 --> 00:02:05,150
a whole lot of
numerical linear algebra

33
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:10,520
