45
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:53,990
So a matrix Q that has --

46
00:02:53,990 --> 00:02:56,680
I'll put these
orthonormal vectors,

47
00:02:56,680 --> 00:03:01,650
q1 will be the first column,
qn will be the n-th column.

48
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:09,610
And I want to say, I want
