86
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,530
Rows times columns.

87
00:05:24,530 --> 00:05:29,390
And in this orthonormal case,
we get the best possible answer,

88
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:30,850
the identity.

89
00:05:30,850 --> 00:05:33,330
OK, so this is --

